=== Hyphenation ===
*nun-cu-pa-tive

===Adjective===
# Publicly or solemnly declaratory. ([[Obs.]])
# Nominal; existing only in name. ([[Obs.]])
# [[Oral]]; not written.
{Nuncupative will} or {testament}, a will or testament made by word of mouth only, before witnesses, as by a soldier or seaman, and depending on oral testimony for [[proof]]. --[[w:Blackstone.]]